articles.title: 20-year-old Ben Shelton upsets Frances Tiafoe to advance to US Open semifinal - CNN
articles.description: Ben Shelton pulled off an upset against fellow American and world No. 10 Frances Tiafoe in four sets in the US Open quarterfinals early Wednesday.
